cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on image generation and translation, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of generative models and unsupervised learning also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The disentangled representation approach is a novel technique that could also be of interest to the graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories.
